{"tid":699250,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"JoJo 的奇妙冒險》彩妝大師「原田忠」與漫畫鬼才「荒木飛呂彥」的跨界合作","createTime":"2018-06-12T11:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T10:58:26.000Z","uid":168698,"like":38,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"bd754cde0306c4df5854305802c46a8b1d546531","tid":699250,"uid":168698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:10:03.000Z","msg":"聽聞荒木係做漫畫家之前係讀緊時裝之後中途轉畫漫畫家下就同日本化妝大師合作<br />\n<img src=\"https://flipermag.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/real-JOJO-07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fflipermag.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F05%2Freal-JOJO-07.jpg&h=52c6ba21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://flipermag.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/real-JOJO-06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fflipermag.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F05%2Freal-JOJO-06.jpg&h=9e6cbabf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然d衣服係gucci既不過gucci都請左荒木去畫畫<br />\n<img src=\"https://pm1.narvii.com/6304/49883d18c1c788fa1252d6cf4ce36a8b39204cec_hq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpm1.narvii.com%2F6304%2F49883d18c1c788fa1252d6cf4ce36a8b39204cec_hq.jpg&h=e93fa3c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pm1.narvii.com/6304/ac992b1e8d89adaaff1a918c7e76bbd2a4e0e7de_hq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpm1.narvii.com%2F6304%2Fac992b1e8d89adaaff1a918c7e76bbd2a4e0e7de_hq.jpg&h=83fbc086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同埋當中角色誇張既動作都係來至時裝雜誌或者廣告<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/5475a116d0782d31af39f47d3a82db02_hd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic3.zhimg.com%2F80%2F5475a116d0782d31af39f47d3a82db02_hd.jpg&h=8915372d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/6352bdb28ef017d04aaa3e6b9861f57b_hd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic2.zhimg.com%2F80%2F6352bdb28ef017d04aaa3e6b9861f57b_hd.jpg&h=171ba329&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/c12ffc9c7b1ea6763f927962bc1c41c1_hd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic3.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fc12ffc9c7b1ea6763f927962bc1c41c1_hd.jpg&h=8f353577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/b222ffd17f63cbd15f67430a89a09bd5_hd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic2.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fb222ffd17f63cbd15f67430a89a09bd5_hd.jpg&h=b2ab91a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所以其實我覺得荒木老師唔做漫畫家都可以係時裝界發展<br />\n老師同gucci創意總監frida giannini合照<br />\n<img src=\"http://images.gamme.com.cn/news2/2014/45/69/p6CVpqKZkKOc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.cn%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F45%2F69%2Fp6CVpqKZkKOc.jpg&h=19971d29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩個都係同年齡大家比較下<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.gameover.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/02125754/page33-600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gameover.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F10%2F02125754%2Fpage33-600x400.jpg&h=2b007a80&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5afcf6c6031411c8dd602cb80cd3d46221f9ffd5","tid":699250,"uid":168698,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:13:27.000Z","msg":"同埋荒木老師其實有兩個女兒<br />\n荒木比原哲夫早一年進入漫畫界，論輩分荒木算是師兄"},{"pid":"15537191ca282fb0c295262bfa80ca4c8c3e18c6","tid":699250,"uid":31174,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:14:45.000Z","msg":"屌你老母幾時出第五部動畫呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c7c0fa604c87c74a6d59755159c6734fc2856ab","tid":699250,"uid":51172,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:16:11.000Z","msg":"荒木老妖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8311ed869deaa3f16110600e01efbafe72fb328","tid":699250,"uid":78773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:16:28.000Z","msg":"不老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12707f6e154508a8b44b6bee3134f27c3f17395c","tid":699250,"uid":168698,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:16:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/mw690/005Pgs9Ely1foex68zecpj30w01kw7f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx4.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F005Pgs9Ely1foex68zecpj30w01kw7f6.jpg&h=2679bc2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依張左邊個位就係荒木老師的太太啦"},{"pid":"ae6e26512c4a0961ae84cdea230985ebdb91b8af","tid":699250,"uid":91325,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:22:42.000Z","msg":"我點都唔會信佢係人類！"},{"pid":"16da78ee86f8a69980beff4d3b12fed6bdcc4368","tid":699250,"uid":168698,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"12707f6e154508a8b44b6bee3134f27c3f17395c","tid":699250,"uid":168698,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:16:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/mw690/005Pgs9Ely1foex68zecpj30w01kw7f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx4.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F005Pgs9Ely1foex68zecpj30w01kw7f6.jpg&h=2679bc2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依張左邊個位就係荒木老師的太太啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:22:55.000Z","msg":"结婚生活如何呢？奥：开始的头10年，感觉就跟初一的小男生生活在一起的感觉非常幼稚，单纯，感觉就是个淘气的孩子有时候甚至会因为&ldquo;自己不是小孩了，不会被人怀疑到&rdquo;而去按别人家的门铃然后逃走。<br />\n<br />\n（笑）非常认生，跟不认识的人在一起都不说话我的朋友来家里玩的时候，他会悄悄把门打开一半，说「啊，又来了！不认识的人！」然后把门紧紧关上。前10年基本就是这个样子。<br />\n<br />\n但是，附近的老爷爷老奶奶都很喜欢他，就像喜欢自己的孙子一样70岁的老爷爷会像叫自己孙子一样地叫他「哟，飞吕彦！身体好吗？」他那时都已经35岁了"},{"pid":"877f45f6afc4d755804d92af362a81f8ff316147","tid":699250,"uid":168698,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/68f62c64gw1dul0fqpbw3j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F68f62c64gw1dul0fqpbw3j.jpg&h=cbe4d9b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近照"},{"pid":"30bd93b1595d5ccc75ff96d565c31ee5f1d905ae","tid":699250,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:28:00.000Z","msg":"